215
00:26:46,140 --> 00:26:48,140
[SPEAKER_02] Bez obzira kak ti deset minuta prođe.

216
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:50,140
[SPEAKER_02] Bez obzira, u početku, bez obzira.

217
00:26:50,140 --> 00:26:57,140
