1169
01:33:09,119 --> 01:33:10,260
[SPEAKER_01] nažalaz sve u korijenu

1170
01:33:10,260 --> 01:33:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] i kad gledamo,

1171
01:33:11,340 --> 01:33:12,220
[SPEAKER_01] koliko imam vremena,

1172
01:33:12,220 --> 01:33:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] imam,

1173
01:33:12,539 --> 01:33:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] daš mi završno,

1174
01:33:14,039 --> 01:33:15,100
[SPEAKER_01] daš mi ono minuticu,

1175
01:33:15,100 --> 01:33:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] dvije još,

1176
01:33:15,579 --> 01:33:16,239
