1181
01:33:21,340 --> 01:33:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] nebrojno puta o evanđeljima

1182
01:33:22,699 --> 01:33:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] čitamo,

1183
01:33:23,180 --> 01:33:24,979
[SPEAKER_01] Isus se povuče u osamu

1184
01:33:24,979 --> 01:33:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ode Isus rano,

1185
01:33:26,000 --> 01:33:27,140
[SPEAKER_01] jutro još za mraka,

1186
01:33:27,140 --> 01:33:28,060
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi molio.

1187
01:33:28,060 --> 01:33:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] Provede noć moja.

1188
01:33:29,279 --> 01:33:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] I provede noć moja,

1189
01:33:30,180 --> 01:33:30,600
[SPEAKER_01] međutim,

1190
01:33:30,600 --> 01:33:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] mi nikad ne znamo

1191
01:33:31,659 --> 01:33:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] kako je to izgledalo.

1192
01:33:33,119 --> 01:33:35,100
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi značilo,

1193
01:33:35,100 --> 01:33:37,100
[SPEAKER_01] Isus nije htio,

1194
01:33:37,100 --> 01:33:39,399
[SPEAKER_01] nije nam htio to pokazati,

1195
01:33:39,399 --> 01:33:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] da ne bi mi toga napravili

1196
01:33:40,760 --> 01:33:41,859
[SPEAKER_01] formu i formulu

1197
01:33:41,859 --> 01:33:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] i tri koraka do uspješne molitve

1198
01:33:43,619 --> 01:33:45,140
