1220
01:34:16,840 --> 01:34:18,119
[SPEAKER_01] to si isto već ti reka,

1221
01:34:18,119 --> 01:34:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] to su već spominjali.

1222
01:34:18,920 --> 01:34:19,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1223
01:34:19,340 --> 01:34:21,600
[SPEAKER_01] ako ti se ne da molit,

1224
01:34:21,600 --> 01:34:23,100
