1225
01:34:23,100 --> 01:34:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] e pa recimo ovo je glupo.

1226
01:34:24,840 --> 01:34:25,800
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ideš molit,

1227
01:34:25,800 --> 01:34:26,779
[SPEAKER_02] ali mu kažeš ne da mi se.

1228
01:34:26,779 --> 01:34:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1229
01:34:27,500 --> 01:34:28,399
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je ono,

1230
01:34:28,399 --> 01:34:29,100
[SPEAKER_01] pojavi se.

1231
01:34:29,100 --> 01:34:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo,

1232
01:34:30,159 --> 01:34:31,680
[SPEAKER_01] dođi kakav jesi,

1233
01:34:31,680 --> 01:34:33,140
[SPEAKER_01] šta god da imaš,

1234
01:34:33,140 --> 01:34:35,560
[SPEAKER_01] ljud sam na muža,

1235
01:34:35,560 --> 01:34:36,060
[SPEAKER_01] na ženu,

1236
01:34:36,060 --> 01:34:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] na posao,

1237
01:34:36,800 --> 01:34:37,939
[SPEAKER_01] na tebe Bože,

1238
01:34:37,939 --> 01:34:38,840
[SPEAKER_01] šta god da imaš,

1239
01:34:38,840 --> 01:34:39,500
[SPEAKER_01] dođi s tim

1240
01:34:39,500 --> 01:34:41,020
[SPEAKER_01] i to mu daje.

1241
01:34:41,020 --> 01:34:43,140
[SPEAKER_01] To je broj dva.

1242
01:34:43,140 --> 01:34:47,300
[SPEAKER_01] I rekao bi broj tri,

1243
