[SPEAKER_01] već kad ovo dvoje savladaš,

1245
01:34:51,420 --> 01:34:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] ono kad već nekako to dođe,

1246
01:34:53,079 --> 01:34:54,439
[SPEAKER_01] broj tri bi rekao,

1247
01:34:54,439 --> 01:34:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] moramo bit,

1248
