[SPEAKER_01] ne znam kada to je lijepo,

1249
01:34:57,239 --> 01:34:57,520
[SPEAKER_01] kažemo,

1250
01:34:57,600 --> 01:34:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] nekako kratko,

1251
01:34:58,340 --> 01:35:01,939
[SPEAKER_01] ali molitva mora bit vođena

1252
01:35:01,939 --> 01:35:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] Duhom Svetim.

1253
