[SPEAKER_00] mi često imamo tu tendenciju

1278
01:35:41,060 --> 01:35:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] gledati kroz ljudske oči

1279
01:35:42,600 --> 01:35:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] i zato ovo što kažeš,

1280
01:35:45,039 --> 01:35:46,659
[SPEAKER_00] možda je vrijednije baš to,

1281
01:35:46,659 --> 01:35:48,020
[SPEAKER_00] da se ti pojaviš,

1282
01:35:48,020 --> 01:35:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] izdvojiš svoje vrijeme

1283
01:35:50,220 --> 01:35:52,260
[SPEAKER_00] i ono,

1284
01:35:52,260 --> 01:35:53,140
