1285
01:35:53,140 --> 01:35:55,600
[SPEAKER_00] možda se mučiš tri mjeseca

1286
01:35:55,600 --> 01:35:56,979
[SPEAKER_00] i uvijek isto,

1287
01:35:56,979 --> 01:35:58,180
[SPEAKER_00] i uvijek isti ishod,

1288
01:35:58,180 --> 01:36:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti ne znaš šta se događa

1289
01:36:00,500 --> 01:36:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] i koje milosti i blagoslove otvaraš

1290
01:36:03,579 --> 01:36:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] u svom srcu,

1291
01:36:04,319 --> 01:36:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] u svom životu za veći prodor milosti.

1292
01:36:07,159 --> 01:36:08,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ti jednostavno ne znaš

1293
01:36:08,479 --> 01:36:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] i ne trebaš ulaziti u odnos sa računicom

1294
01:36:11,260 --> 01:36:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] da da mučiš ću se tako da dobijem ne,

1295
01:36:13,279 --> 01:36:15,899
[SPEAKER_00] nego ulaziš u odnos zbog odnosa,

1296
01:36:15,899 --> 01:36:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] zbog njega.

1297
01:36:16,539 --> 01:36:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, htjela bih samo to reći,

1298
01:36:19,380 --> 01:36:21,859
[SPEAKER_00] da nipošto se ne stavlja

1299
01:36:21,859 --> 01:36:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] i u to neke opipljive okvire,

1300
01:36:24,819 --> 01:36:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi ne znamo,

1301
01:36:26,720 --> 01:36:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] koliko može biti vrijedniji taj naš napor

1302
01:36:31,039 --> 01:36:34,020
[SPEAKER_00] da odvojim vrijeme,

1303
01:36:34,020 --> 01:36:35,560
[SPEAKER_00] iako mi je teško,

1304
01:36:35,560 --> 01:36:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] iako ništa ne osjećam,

1305
01:36:37,000 --> 01:36:38,939
[SPEAKER_00] kako Bog na to gleda.

1306
01:36:38,939 --> 01:36:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem da Bog na to gleda

1307
01:36:42,300 --> 01:36:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] s velikim ponosom

1308
01:36:44,260 --> 01:36:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] i da se milost probija ogromno,

1309
01:36:47,920 --> 01:36:49,159
[SPEAKER_00] ogromno na tvoj život.

1310
01:36:49,159 --> 01:36:50,680
[SPEAKER_00] Bravo.

1311
01:36:50,680 --> 01:36:53,840
[SPEAKER_02] Da, hvala vam.

1312
01:36:53,840 --> 01:36:55,140
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam kaj bih rekao drugo.

1313
01:36:55,140 --> 01:36:57,399
[SPEAKER_02] Vrš vam hvala.

1314
01:36:57,399 --> 01:37:00,439
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala na neki način

1315
