[SPEAKER_02] sami u odnosu s Bogom,

1317
01:37:03,319 --> 01:37:05,180
[SPEAKER_02] pa sad mi to možemo

1318
01:37:05,180 --> 01:37:06,800
[SPEAKER_02] naučiti nekaj od vas,

1319
01:37:06,800 --> 01:37:08,939
[SPEAKER_02] a da nije da moramo sami prolaziti.

1320
01:37:08,939 --> 01:37:10,880
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala vam kaj ste odvojili vrijeme,

1321
01:37:10,880 --> 01:37:11,859
[SPEAKER_02] kaj ste tu došli

1322
01:37:11,859 --> 01:37:14,420
[SPEAKER_02] i sa mnom ste se rado odazvali.

1323
01:37:14,420 --> 01:37:15,260
[SPEAKER_02] Ja to znam,

1324
01:37:15,260 --> 01:37:17,260
[SPEAKER_02] tako da, evo,

1325
01:37:17,260 --> 01:37:18,619
[SPEAKER_02] baš vas je bilo blagoslovo imati.

1326
01:37:18,619 --> 01:37:21,119
[SPEAKER_02] Dragi naši prijatelji,

1327
01:37:21,119 --> 01:37:22,739
[SPEAKER_02] prije nego što odjavimo

1328
01:37:22,739 --> 01:37:23,939
[SPEAKER_02] ovu emisiju,

1329
01:37:23,939 --> 01:37:26,239
[SPEAKER_02] kao što ste već čuli dva puta,

1330
01:37:26,239 --> 01:37:28,800
[SPEAKER_02] Matej je napisao knjigu

1331
01:37:28,800 --> 01:37:30,340
[SPEAKER_02] Zove Sjeda na jedan sa Bogom.

1332
01:37:30,340 --> 01:37:33,460
[SPEAKER_02] može se kupiti putem web shopa

1333
01:37:33,460 --> 01:37:34,420
[SPEAKER_02] naše zajednice.

1334
01:37:34,420 --> 01:37:37,779
[SPEAKER_02] Ja znam puno ljudi

1335
01:37:37,779 --> 01:37:39,500
[SPEAKER_02] koji ju imaju.

1336
01:37:39,500 --> 01:37:41,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam sve veri,

1337
01:37:41,039 --> 01:37:42,000
[SPEAKER_02] imamo dva primjerka

1338
01:37:42,000 --> 01:37:42,600
[SPEAKER_02] i evo, stvarno,

1339
01:37:42,600 --> 01:37:43,539
[SPEAKER_02] svima je preporučamo.

1340
01:37:43,539 --> 01:37:45,079
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, možete ne baviti

1341
01:37:45,079 --> 01:37:47,079
[SPEAKER_02] preko web shopa Bože pobjede.

1342
01:37:47,079 --> 01:37:49,739
[SPEAKER_02] I druga vrlo važna stvar je,

1343
