[SPEAKER_02] organizira večer slavljenja

1347
01:37:56,380 --> 01:37:58,260
[SPEAKER_02] slavljenja ovoga puta

1348
01:37:58,260 --> 01:37:59,420
[SPEAKER_02] na jugu,

1349
01:37:59,420 --> 01:38:00,199
[SPEAKER_02] u Splitu,

1350
01:38:00,199 --> 01:38:02,199
[SPEAKER_02] 14. listopada

1351
01:38:02,199 --> 01:38:03,500
[SPEAKER_02] u dvorani Gripe.

1352
01:38:03,500 --> 01:38:06,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ko nije kupio kartu,

1353
01:38:06,000 --> 01:38:08,180
[SPEAKER_02] stigne još kratko koliko ih ima

1354
01:38:08,180 --> 01:38:09,779
[SPEAKER_02] i nadam se da se vidimo.

1355
01:38:09,779 --> 01:38:11,420
[SPEAKER_02] Svi ćemo biti tamo.

1356
01:38:12,699 --> 01:38:13,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ako neko neće,

1357
01:38:13,460 --> 01:38:14,119
[SPEAKER_02] vjerojatno sad neće

1358
01:38:14,119 --> 01:38:15,060
[SPEAKER_02] to nisi reći,

1359
01:38:15,060 --> 01:38:16,260
[SPEAKER_02] ali svi ćemo biti tamo.

1360
01:38:16,260 --> 01:38:17,359
[SPEAKER_02] Tak da evo,

1361
01:38:17,359 --> 01:38:18,960
[SPEAKER_02] vidimo svijedući mjesec.

1362
01:38:18,960 --> 01:38:21,260
[SPEAKER_02] Pratite sve naše sadržaje

1363
01:38:21,260 --> 01:38:23,279
